msgstr " "

msgctxt "an9.26:3.10"
msgid "‘yato kho, āvuso, bhikkhuno cetasā cittaṃ suparicitaṃ hoti, tassetaṃ bhikkhuno kallaṃ veyyākaraṇāya—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an9.26:3.11"
msgid "khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāmī’”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an9.26:4.1"
msgid "Tatiyampi kho āyasmā candikāputto bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "And for a third time Venerable Candikāputta addressed the mendicants … "

